data.description: Farmhouse Ready! Farmhouse Decor! Farmhouse Tiles and Farmhouse doors. Located in a stellar location in the heart of Saks. The family room and dining room are just off the kitchen featuring a never-ending view of the huge fenced backyard. Just off the dining room, open up to the backyard that offers the pathway to romantic getaways at home, perfect for star gazing, backyard Bar B Qs and family & friend get-togethers! Three bedrooms upstairs with huge closets and Master Oasis has freshly done in Jan 2022, New hot Water heater, new HVAC, new floors in downstairs, new plumbing in downstairs. One car carport, and one car garage. The one-car garage was a recently started project to be turned into a man cave.  What more can you ask for in this 4 bedroom 3 full bath home? 100% Financing is Available for those who qualify.
